<abstract><t>This document describes the architecture and requirements for the Messaging Layer Security (MLS) protocol.  MLS provides a security layer for group messaging applications with from two to a large number of clients.  It is meant to protect against eavesdropping, tampering, and message forgery.</t></abstract>

